Notes rowspan=21989 rowspan=21990 rowspan=21993 rowspan=31996 rowspan=22001 rowspan=22005 rowspan=22013 rowspan=32016 AWARDS AND NOMINATIONS Section::::Awards and nominations .
Kudrow has been honored with numerous accolades over her career .
For her role in the sitcom [ [ Friends ] ] , she received six nominations at the [ [ Primetime Emmy Award]]s , winning in 1996 for [ [ Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Supporting Actress in a Comedy SeriesOutstanding Supporting Actress in a Comedy Series ] ] .
Kudrow has also received twelve nominations and two wins at the [ [ Screen Actors Guild Award]]s , as well as one win and eight nominations at the [ [ American Comedy Awards ] ] .
